        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a485" ANNOTATION_REF="a194">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>at theirs, he spoiled her, whatever she wanted, people were not wearing gold, she had bracelets like this, with holes and stones</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a486" ANNOTATION_REF="a195">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>he made them for her (the bracelets) and made her wear them, one sang about her Oh Nura, some problems will be in your life and will stay with you and will not go away  -----</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
