        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a538" ANNOTATION_REF="a215">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh dust, I want to escape (run away); I don't know what to do. She said, 'It's me and you.'</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
